Sending a Model Best Practices

1. Copy the model file out of the directory to the Desktop or other specific file

2. Open the file and make sure to click "Audit" and "Detach from Central" Note that "Audit" does not provide feed back and make take a while to complete.

3. Open the model and save.

4. Under the "Mange" tab select "Manage Links". Remove all links that are not being sent with the model.

5. Still under the "Manage" tab, select "Purge all Unused" and select ok. You may want to repeat the process at least twice.
